  "description": "Vendor-neutral prompt operating system for Claude Code / Codex / Gemini. Structured Phase 0→5 director protocol: environment lock → deep inventory → parallel specialist evidence → did-you-know discovery → synthesis → manager verdict. Audit, govern, and scaffold full-stack SaaS with 24 sector packs, 8 rule packs, ~100 anti-pattern bullets (19 numbered AP-NN), 22 governance docs, 27 specialist agents, 9 slash-commands, 8 skills, 33 runtime rules, 27 scaffolder templates. Deep-inventory discipline rejects folder dumps; parallel specialist dispatch rejects single-agent evidence; validation gate rejects unverified signoff.",
